description:
1 x Clear Screen

Please specify which screen you would like:

Standard Screen
Manufactured to directly replace your original screen. Our standard screens are all pre-drilled and will fit using all your original fixings. A stylish addition to any motorcycle.



Double Bubble Race Screen
These have been designed in conjunction with teams such as BSB Champions Airwaves Yamaha and Superstock Champions TAS Relentless Suzuki, where a taller screen was requested for the race track. We were looking to enhance the aerodynamics of the bike and increase the air pocket behind the screen, as well as giving the rider greater protection at high speed (not over 70 mph of course). These race screens are not pre-drilled .

description:
1 x Clear Screen

Please specify which screen you would like:

Standard Screen
Manufactured to directly replace your original screen. Our standard screens are all pre-drilled and will fit using all your original fixings. A stylish addition to any motorcycle.

Tall Screen
Designed to be taller than the original screen and re-direct the air flow higher over the bike. These are ideal for sports or touring use and will fit onto the original fixing points however are not pre-drilled.

Double Bubble Race Screen
These have been designed in conjunction with teams such as BSB Champions Airwaves Yamaha and Superstock Champions TAS Relentless Suzuki, where a taller screen was requested for the race track. We were looking to enhance the aerodynamics of the bike and increase the air pocket behind the screen, as well as giving the rider greater protection at high speed (not over 70 mph of course). These race screens are not pre-drilled .

description:
Motoholders: Race Rear Subframes and Front Subframe / Clock Brackets
Available in Black or Silver

Excellent engineering with lightweight material– manufactured from aerospace grade aluminium
Engineered fitment for standard battery trays
Guaranteed fitment with all CRC race fairings
Standard fitment for clocks / tachos

Motoholders offer the latest technology in premium race rear subframes and front subframe / clock brackets.  As used by teams in World Superbikes, British Superbikes and road racing teams, these subframes are chosen for their lightweight design and fitment which is unseen elsewhere.
